  "texts": [
    "Embedding Dynamic Linking: Incorporate the dynamic linking mechanism (DLM) into GPT-Neo (G), enabling access to a broad array of external data sources (S).G ← G + DLM(S)(5)2.",
    "Data Transformation: Develop a custom data transformation layer (DT L) to convert external data (D ext) into a format compatible with GPT-Neo's internal data representation (D int).D int = DT L(D ext)(6)3.",
    "Refresh Cycles: Introduce periodic refresh cycles (RC), where GPT-Neo is fine-tuned with newly integrated data, to ensure the model's knowledge remains current.G new = RC(G, D int)(7)4.",
